article.description: — Michael Forrest posted 14 points as Florida Atlantic defeated Southern Miss 69-60 on Friday night.
article.headline: Forrest scores 14 to carry FAU over Southern Miss 69-60
article.linkText: Forrest scores 14 to carry FAU over Southern Miss 69-60
article.story: HATTIESBURG, Miss. -- — Michael Forrest posted 14 points as Florida Atlantic defeated Southern Miss 69-60 on Friday night. Jailyn Ingram had 12 points for Florida Atlantic (9-9, 4-5 Conference USA). Johnell Davis added 10 points. Karlis Silins had 10 points. LaDavius Draine had 17 points for the Golden Eagles (8-15, 4-12). Justin Johnson added 11 points. Tyler Stevenson had 11 points and eight rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
